              "id": "c3ba9553-2570-4aab-ad46-325d5bc851b6",
              "name": "response",
              "value": "=🎯 MATCH SCORE: {{ $json.score }}/100\n\n📋 DECISION: {{ $json.desision }}\n\n💡 WHY:\n{{ $json.reasons }}\n\n⚠️ MISSING SKILLS:\n{{ $json[\"missing skills\"] }}\n\n🚀 NEXT STEP:\n{{ $json[\"next step\"] }}",
